  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, mix Greek yogurt with garlic powder and oregano.",
    "Stir in lemon juice to taste. Add sesame seeds for crunchiness, then add olive oil gradually while mixing until desired consistency is reached.",
    "Prepare the vegetables: slice cucumbers, onion, and tomatoes thinly.",
    "In a serving dish, place tomato slices on bottom layer, followed by evenly distributed cucumber, onion, and feta cheese pieces. Drizzle over Greek yogurt dressing mixture to evenly coat.",
    "Garnish with additional chopped fresh dill before serving."
